# demos/agents.tape — Agents and themes
Output demos/agents.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "hello"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "/agent bofh"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "why is my code slow?"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "/agent architect"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "design a cache layer for this service"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "/theme hacker"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "exit"
Enter
